	&lt;li&gt;Allahabad Bank&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Bank of Baroda&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Bank of India&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Bank of Maharashtra&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Central Bank of India&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Dena Bank&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Indian Bank&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Indian Overseas Bank&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Punjab National Bank&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Syndicate Bank&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Union Bank of India&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;United Bank of India&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Nationalisation of 6 more Commercial Banks&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Government of India nationalised 6 more commercial banks in 1980. The banks that were nationalised were:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Andhra Bank&lt;/li&gt;
